Well...

333
00:23:20,680 --> 00:23:22,720
Maybe someone who likes to judge people from their looks.

334
00:23:25,390 --> 00:23:26,900
People who judge others from their looks.

335
00:23:28,720 --> 00:23:29,170
So,

336
00:23:30,500 --> 00:23:32,000
