337
00:23:34,350 --> 00:23:34,630
Huh?

338
00:23:37,250 --> 00:23:38,720
Someone with whom I feel comfortable

339
00:23:41,590 --> 00:23:43,040
and have something in common.

340
00:23:45,880 --> 00:23:47,200
It'll be better

341
00:23:47,880 --> 00:23:48,480
