357
00:25:12,250 --> 00:25:14,130
I hope you meet that person soon.

358
00:25:17,450 --> 00:25:20,280
Thank you so much for today, Brother Yang. See you tomorrow.

359
00:25:22,490 --> 00:25:24,490
Oh, right. We won't see each other tomorrow.

360
00:25:24,710 --> 00:25:28,210
I'll get going then. Thank you. Bye. Bye.

