00:27:47,240 --> 00:27:49,280
I remember you like baseball.

366
00:27:49,750 --> 00:27:51,570
So I wanted to invite you to play catch.

367
00:27:53,880 --> 00:27:57,210
You probably haven't played it since you came to Thailand.

368
00:27:57,740 --> 00:27:59,580
So I wanted to invite you to play with me.

369
00:28:48,600 --> 00:28:49,300
Good luck.

370
00:28:50,400 --> 00:28:51,780
Ask me if you have any questions.

371
00:29:21,490 --> 00:29:23,450
-Phumjai. -Hi, Tammy.

372
00:29:23,750 --> 00:29:25,140
Where should we go?

373
00:29:25,490 --> 00:29:26,950
I want to go shopping today.

374
00:29:26,950 --> 00:29:28,970
You want to go shopping. Follow me.

375
00:29:28,970 --> 00:29:30,460
Okay.

376
00:29:35,830 --> 00:29:36,700
Where did they go?

377
00:29:36,820 --> 00:29:39,040
I know, right? We were following them just now.

378
00:29:40,550 --> 00:29:42,710
What should we do now?

379
00:29:46,230 --> 00:29:46,980
How about this?

380
00:29:47,930 --> 00:29:48,950
Let's follow them there.

381
00:29:49,620 --> 00:29:50,870
We'll keep tracking them if we see them.

382
00:29:51,800 --> 00:29:52,970
But if we don't see them,

383
00:29:53,850 --> 00:29:54,940
