384
00:29:55,390 --> 00:29:55,840
Okay?

385
00:29:57,600 --> 00:29:59,610
We've been disguised like this.

386
00:30:00,050 --> 00:30:01,260
No one can recognize us.

387
00:30:01,620 --> 00:30:03,310
Okay, Phumjai?

388
00:30:04,680 --> 00:30:06,430
Is that okay?

389
00:30:07,900 --> 00:30:08,780
But even

390
00:30:09,670 --> 00:30:11,180
someone we think will always be by our side

391
00:30:12,190 --> 00:30:13,050
may leave us

392
00:30:14,110 --> 00:30:15,240
one day.

393
00:30:19,360 --> 00:30:20,340
Okay, Phumjai?

394
00:30:20,760 --> 00:30:23,110
You're not in their way anyway.

395
00:30:23,740 --> 00:30:24,440
Is that okay?

396
00:30:27,790 --> 00:30:28,420
All right.

397
00:30:29,240 --> 00:30:30,330
Let's go.

398
00:30:30,960 --> 00:30:32,990
Let's go, Tag. Let's go.

399
00:30:33,780 --> 00:30:34,750
Oh, follow me.

400
00:30:56,450 --> 00:30:59,610
Qi'er, look.

401
00:31:00,040 --> 00:31:03,010
Hey, Tammy's post.

402
00:31:03,250 --> 00:31:05,280
-Is this Phumjai? -Let me see.

403
00:31:05,600 --> 00:31:05,900
Hey.

404
00:31:06,330 --> 00:31:09,230
-Here. -It is him.

405
00:31:09,480 --> 00:31:11,950
They're together.

406
00:32:11,990 --> 00:32:14,710
What a beautiful view!

407
00:32:14,870 --> 00:32:17,540
Is this the scenery on the postcard that Phumjai mentioned?

408
00:32:17,660 --> 00:32:19,000
It is.

409
00:32:19,230 --> 00:32:20,860
Yeah, the view is really beautiful.

410
00:32:20,860 --> 00:32:24,690
-Yes. -Think about it. It'd be nice

411
00:32:25,010 --> 00:32:28,130
