412
00:32:38,030 --> 00:32:40,080
We lost them anyway.

413
00:32:40,730 --> 00:32:42,550
But we're here on a date, aren't we?

414
00:32:43,530 --> 00:32:44,170
Isn't it nice?

415
00:32:46,720 --> 00:32:47,040
Yeah.

416
00:32:48,710 --> 00:32:49,490
Like this.

417
00:32:50,010 --> 00:32:52,060
