424
00:33:09,290 --> 00:33:09,760
That's all.

425
00:33:10,230 --> 00:33:10,890
You said that.

426
00:33:11,370 --> 00:33:11,830
Yes.

427
00:33:13,060 --> 00:33:13,930
Then...

428
00:33:14,460 --> 00:33:16,630
Can we not pretend when I want to go on a date next time?

429
00:33:18,350 --> 00:33:19,090
Why?

430
00:33:20,120 --> 00:33:21,190
Don't I look cool this way?

431
00:33:22,870 --> 00:33:26,190
Well, I just think Phumjai has a job now.

432
00:33:26,710 --> 00:33:28,170
And he's getting better and better.

433
00:33:28,970 --> 00:33:30,410
I think we can make it public.

434
00:33:32,240 --> 00:33:33,650
Is that okay?

435
00:33:36,630 --> 00:33:37,010
Sure.

436
00:33:38,120 --> 00:33:38,540
Really?

437
00:33:39,840 --> 00:33:40,640
But

438
00:33:42,070 --> 00:33:43,010
