439
00:33:45,630 --> 00:33:46,000
Okay.

440
00:34:15,300 --> 00:34:15,889
Brother Yang,

441
00:34:17,010 --> 00:34:17,989
I have something to tell you.

442
00:34:19,179 --> 00:34:19,540
What?

443
00:34:20,830 --> 00:34:22,780
Are you here to show off your date with Tammy?

444
00:34:23,900 --> 00:34:24,210
Huh?

445
00:34:24,820 --> 00:34:26,590
So you didn't have time to read my texts.

446
00:34:27,760 --> 00:34:28,810
The date went well.

447
00:34:29,550 --> 00:34:32,100
But... Why isn't it what I thought it would be?

448
00:34:34,280 --> 00:34:34,719
Why?

449
00:34:35,739 --> 00:34:37,420
You had a date with someone you like.

450
00:34:38,179 --> 00:34:39,000
Aren't you happy?

451
00:34:42,460 --> 00:34:43,929
I don't know.

452
00:34:45,310 --> 00:34:45,639
But

453
00:34:46,380 --> 00:34:47,420
I feel strange.

454
00:34:52,580 --> 00:34:52,949
Okay.

455
00:35:00,910 --> 00:35:02,040
When we were eating together,

456
